==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Burdensome
<hw>Bur"den*some</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Grievous to be
borne; causing uneasiness or fatigue; oppressive.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The debt immense of endless gratitude⟦br⟧
So <qex>burdensome</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Heavy; weighty; cumbersome; onerous; grievous;
oppressive; troublesome.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Bur"den*some*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Bur"den*some*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Burdock</ent>⟦br⟧
